headline: Do You Believe in the Growth Potential of Targa Resources Corp. (TRGP)?
summary: Oakmark Funds, advised by Harris Associates, released its “Oakmark Fund” third-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. In the third quarter, the fund underperformed its benchmark, the S&P 500 Index, but outperformed the benchmark since inception.
